    "text": [
        "Dear Lincy,",
        "I hope you are keeping fine. As I hinted at last Friday mine and Joseph\u2019s leaves are approved for one month. We will be leaving from here by Thursday evening 8 in the evening. Flight is at 12 O\u2019 Clock in the morning. As the keys are already with you, it is not necessary that you to come.",
        "There are some perishable food items like yoghurt, egg, milk, cheese, vegetables, meat and fish in the refrigerator. Please make sure to collect those and consume at the earliest. Please double check that all the switches are off.",
        "Regarding the aquarium, feed the fishes in every two days. Please make sure to change the water every week. Next is about watering of indoor plants, the water sprayer is in the balcony. If you can do it in every two days, that would be better.  Please make sure to start the car upon your convenience ask the security to wash regularly, Key is hanging in the kitchen",
        "If anything please Watsapp in the UAE number + 971556980084 or call on + 919961373964.",
        "See you on April 27th.",
        "Thanks & regards",
        "Maria"
